##Self-report | Wuhan University student cured new coronary pneumonia at home

The papernews

The function introduction, has the connotation the current politics new media

Intern, Liu Xu, _ paper _ journalist, Yu Yan

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
On January 29, Jia Hu (not his real name) tested double positive. All figures in this article are provided by the respondents

On February 7th, after 20 days of isolation at home, Jia Hu (not his real name) came back negative for nucleic acid, and he finally beat the new pneumonia.

Jia Hu was deeply moved by all the experiences he had during his illness. He said that after recovery, the most want to do is to listen to a idol bridge caoxiang concert.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
On February 7, Jia Hu (not his real name) tested double negative.

Jia Hu, 21, is a junior at a university in Wuhan, majoring in English with a minor in Japanese. Love the second dimension of his winter vacation took a language class to learn Japanese, ready to go to Japan after graduation to engage in the sound industry.

At first, Jia thought it was just a common cold, but he didn't care. By Jan. 21, the pain had not subsided, and reports of the outbreak began to accumulate. Jia and his family realized that "something might be wrong, " and sought medical help immediately. On Jan. 29, jia Hu's nucleic acid test results showed a double-positive, was officially diagnosed as infected with new crown pneumonia.

After the diagnosis, the hospital gave out the drug free of charge, cleats, Jia Hu at home isolation, medication. After 20 days, Jia finally recovered. He told The Paper news (www.thepaper.cn ) that during the experience, special thanks were given to the medical staff.

While in the hospital, he had noticed a detail, the doctor's isolation clothing brand changed every few days, Dupont, steady, 3m, kimberly..

"I didn't know until I asked, the hospital had already run out of procurement. These are all donated by society. They are all heroes, " Jia said.

Jia Hu dictation

"It was a rough couple of days. "

On January 17, when I was in language school, I felt sore all over and probably had a fever. Thinking it was just a common cold, I started taking Tylenol, and now that I think about it, Thnoz's soothing effects probably masked the problem, and I regret it.

At noon on January 21, feeling very sore, I contacted my father, who was keenly aware that something might be wrong and told me to hurry home. At home in the evening temperature, low-grade fever, but my body still do not feel special, because eat hot pot, my mother proposed later temperature, if still low-grade fever to the hospital. At 11:00 pm he found that his fever was still low and went to Tongji Hospital immediately.

After that, I saw a lot of people. For the first time, I saw the doctor in isolation suit. The medical records were piled up. I felt something was wrong. So I decided to go to Wuhan Lung Hospital Not far away.

Well after the emergency room, I checked the blood routine, liver function, lung CT, CT results the same night, Patchy Shadow, double lower lung infection. The next day out of the liver function showed that everything is normal, blood routine is all normal, but high-sensitivity c-reactive protein (CRP) .

Around January 25, I gradually began to cough, with a very small amount of sputum that was difficult to cough up. I went to Wuhan Lung Hospital for a follow-up check, the results showed that the disease became worse, the infection spread to the whole lung. A RISE IN CRP usually indicates a worsening of an acute infection. My CRP shot up to 39.76, and the doctor prescribed an infusion.

Getting out of bed the next day was particularly difficult, as I shivered and took my temperature over 39 degrees. Started a home quarantine, stayed in his room and barely came out.

When the 28th reexamination, my lung infection condition has improved, after the expert group consultation gave me the kit test qualification.

On January 29, my kit tested positive for the new coronavirus and was officially diagnosed. The hospital distributed free HIV antiretroviral drug cleats for five days. As my condition continued to improve, hospital beds are tight, the doctor told me to go home to continue isolation, infusion stopped, oral medicine still continue to take.

Those days really too uncomfortable, and vomiting and diarrhea, coughing and coughing my whole back is pain, there is no appetite. But I can't fight it without food, so I force myself to eat.

"The only thing I want to do when I'm cured is go to my idol's concert. "

When I got better, I went back to the kit. Two separate tests, both negative. I'm cured. Looking back on the healing experience, I was really lucky to come back and try harder to live.

I'm doing just fine now, with no residual effects, basically the same as before. When the epidemic is over, the last thing I want to do is go to a concert by my idol, chae-heung. During my illness, I saw the animation of the voice of my idol, which gave me great encouragement.

After the city closed, the city traffic stopped, many people without conditions can not go to the hospital, delayed the illness, I feel very uncomfortable, I am only glad that we have a car at home. In addition, in the course of treatment also encountered a lot of let me more shocked, more sad things.

Once in the hospital infusion, I am next to an old GRANDPA arm swollen very high, scared me. Probably because old people's blood vessels are more fragile, run off the needle. The old man had no one to accompany him, and there were so many patients that the nurses did not notice. I quickly help him to call the nurse, a needle pulled, the back of GRANDPA's hands full of blood, really can not bear to see.

Another time I saw an old woman in her eighty getting oxygen in her hospital bed. The sound of her inhaling oxygen seemed to Moan, and I could feel it in my ears. I couldn't forget it.

I hope the patients are at peace. Don't take it out on the doctors and nurses. They're all fighting for their lives on the front line. When I was in the hospital, I also noticed a detail, the doctor's isolation clothing brand will change every few days, Dupont, moderate, 3m, Kimberly, ... only to find out that the hospital procurement has been used up, these are donated by the community, they are heroes.
